description: Leading Edge Materials Corp. engages in the exploration and development of resource properties. The company is headquartered in Vancouver, British Columbia. The company went IPO on 2011-06-10. The firm's portfolio of projects includes the Woxna Graphite mine in Sweden, Norra Karr rare earth element (REE) project in Sweden and approximately 51% owned Bihor Sud Nickel Cobalt exploration alliance in Romania. The Woxna Project is located approximately eight kilometers west-north-west of the town of Edsbyn, northwest of the city of Gavle in Central Sweden. Woxna Graphite AB, a subsidiary of the Company, owns approximately four mining concessions over graphite deposits (the Kringelgruven graphite deposit, Gropabo graphite deposit and Mattsmyra graphite deposit) located along approximately 40 kilometers (km) trend in central Sweden. Norra Karr REE project is located in southern Sweden approximately 300km south west (SW) of Stockholm.
name: Leading Edge Materials Corp
